Sue Carol https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sue_Carol 0 Sue Carol (October 30, 1906 – February 4, 1982) was an American actress and talent agent. While at a social function in Los Angeles in 1927, a director offered her a part in a film. She took it and began playing minor parts. Carol's film career lasted from the late 1920s into the 1930s; when it ended, she became a talent agent. The last of her three marriages was to one of her clients, Alan Ladd, from 1942 until his death in 1964. Sue_Carol ( October_30_,_1906 – February_4_,_1982 ) was an_American_actress_and_talent_agent .
